OL,5,G1650 Wales' Home of the Year
OL,6,     F1/6. In Mid Wales and the valleys,
OL,7,     Fthe judges choose between a
OL,8,     F17th-century cottage in Neath, a
OL,9,     Ffarmhouse renovation in Lampeter
OL,10,     Fand a colourful end-of-terrace
OL,11,     Fhouse in Aberystwyth.
OL,12,G1720 21st Century TV with Lucy Owen
OL,13,     F10/10. Lucy Owen takes a personal
OL,14,     Ftrip through the BBC Wales news
OL,15,     Fand entertainment archives of
OL,16,     F2009, including BBC Wales
OL,17,     Fpresenters taking part in a
OL,18,     FStrictly dance-off for Children in
OL,19,     FNeed.
